name: Feline - DEMO
description:
This is a platformer adventure with our beloved cute werecat, Feline. Run, jump, and use Feline's special skills to overcome every obstacle.

Features:
★ Three different languages available: Indonesian, English, and Japanese.
★ Full voiced (in Indonesian language).
★ Get new adorable costumes for Feline.
★ Interesting and heartwarming story of the heroine.

Minimum requirement:

  • Chipset LEADCORE quad-core @1,5Ghz
  • RAM 1 GB
  • GPU MALI T-628
  • ANDROID KITKAT

Lower spec device might be able to play. Just test it, it's free. :)

Also if you encounter any bug please report it to link below:
s.id/felinebug
